        <div class="course-content-block" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2>About the Program</h2>
          <p>
            The Post Basic Bachelor of Science in Nursing is a two-year degree
            program designed exclusively for registered nurses who hold a GNM
            diploma and wish to upgrade to a bachelor's degree.
          </p>
          <p>
            This program deepens clinical knowledge, enhances leadership skills,
            and opens doors to senior nursing roles, teaching positions and
            specialised career paths in India and internationally.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="course-content-block" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
          <ul class="course-list">
            <li>Must hold a GNM diploma from a recognised institution</li>
            <li>Minimum one year of work experience as a registered nurse</li>
            <li>Registered with State Nursing Council</li>
            <li>Passed 10+2 or equivalent from a recognised board</li>
            <li>Medically fit as per INC norms</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="course-content-block" data-aos="fade-up">
